        When executing query:
            """
            USING HOPS LIMIT 5 MATCH p=(a)-[:CONNECTED *]->(e) RETURN p
            """
        Then the result should be:
            | p                                                                                                      |
            | <(:Node {name: 'A'})-[:CONNECTED]->(:Node {name: 'B'})>                                                |
